description: Charlie adores their versatile, 60” fretwork sideboard. They never knew a front tiered credenza could look so smart. Charlie loves the three drawers that run on telescoping drawer glides; such a smooth unit! The fretwork detailing on the four cabinet doors speak to Charlie. “Modern, traditional, farmhouse, you name it,” they whisper. “We’ll fit any style you love.” Most of all Charlie appreciates that this storage sideboard also serves as an entertainment center. Its flat top can accommodate TVs up to 65” and with cord management, Charlie never has to worry about messy cables. So, be like Charlie and pop this nifty model anywhere you like to fill all your organizational needs.
